is a template that includes features for the design and look of your site. Many beginners search for simple themes that aren&#8217;t bloated with extra features so they can quickly set up and launch their website without asking help from expensive web [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/\">43 Simple WordPress Themes to Easily Start a Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54234:\"<p>Do you want a simple WordPress theme for your WordPress website? A theme is a template that includes features for the design and look of your site. Many beginners search for simple themes that aren&#8217;t bloated with extra features so they can quickly set up and launch their website without asking help from expensive web developers; however, with so many themes available, finding the right one can prove frustrating.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why, in this article, we&#8217;ll share our handpicked list of the 43 best simple WordPress themes so you can choose one and start your website in no time flat.</p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-3\">Quick Info: Top 5 Simple WordPress Themes</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-3\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Theme</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Uniqueness</th><th class=\"column-4\">Released by</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Portfolio Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Workstation Pro</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$99.95</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best for Displaying Hero Images</td><td class=\"column-4\">StudioPress</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Corner</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">from $35 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Minimalist Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">CSS Igniter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Shape</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$58 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Portfolio Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">Tesla Themes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Ambiance Pro</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$99.95</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Full-width/ No Sidebar Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">StudioPress</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Enterprise</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$58 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Corporate Theme with Built-in Forums</td><td class=\"column-4\">Tesla Themes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-3 from cache -->\n<h3>Creating a Website with a Simple WordPress Theme</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared-2018/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared (2018)\">popular website builder</a> in the world. Many of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">biggest brands are using WordPress actively</a> on their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites. First, there&#8217;s WordPress.com, which is a hosted solution. Then, there&#8217;s WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted platform.</p>\n<p>To create a simple website, you&#8217;ll need to select self-hosted WordPress.org. But, before you start, you&#8217;ll also need to buy a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"Whats the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s a well-renowned web hosting company, and is also officially recommended by WordPress.org.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering our users a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on the web hosting.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> has agreed to provide you, as an IsItWP reader, a web hosting plan with 60% off on the regular hosting price. You can start your website for just $2.75 per month. </p>\n<p>After purchasing the web hosting, you can follow our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>Ready? Next, scroll through our handpicked list of simple WordPress themes choose the best one for your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Workstation Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation.jpg\" alt=\"Workstation Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224140\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Workstation Pro is a simple WordPress theme for your personal and professional websites. It&#8217;s built on the well-known Genesis framework which gives the theme a solid foundation. It has an easy-to-use options panel and you can also customize the theme settings with the live preview. The homepage and other pages are widget-based, so you can easily drag and drop features to develop your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Corner</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner.jpg\" alt=\"Corner\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224141\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Corner is a beautiful WordPress theme with all the useful features you need for your website. It&#8217;s not bloated with features like the big themes and has a simple design. It comes with a widget-based layout to easily drag and drop widgets on the homepage and other pages. Corner has multiple color schemes, and a lot of custom settings for WordPress websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Shape</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape.jpg\" alt=\"Shape\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224142\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Shape is a modern WordPress theme for the fitness, health, photography, images, and other websites. It supports a grid-based layout to showcase your photos. It works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">best image gallery plugins</a> to create filterable galleries in WordPress. Shape has homepage sections like portfolio, services, clients, team, and more. It comes with custom widgets, color options, multiple layouts, and Google Maps integration.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Ambiance Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro.jpg\" alt=\"Ambiance Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224143\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ambiance Pro is a stylish WordPress theme with widget ready layout. You can easily drag and drop widgets to the homepage with multiple widget areas. This theme is built on the popular Genesis framework. It has unlimited color choices, page templates, gallery post formats, and more. Ambiance Pro is easy to set up and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">optimized for SEO</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Enterprise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise.jpg\" alt=\"Enterprise\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224134\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Enterprise is a WordPress theme for business and professional websites. It has a simple and neat design with multiple sections on the homepage to create a beautiful website. It comes with pricing tables, FAQs section, portfolio section, services section, and a homepage <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins for 2018 (Compared)\">image slider</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/maxwell/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Maxwell\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Maxwell</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/maxwell/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Maxwell\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell.jpg\" alt=\"Maxwell\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224135\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Maxwell is a simple WordPress theme designed specifically for news and magazine blogs. It enables you to display your featured posts with images on the homepage. It comes with 2 navigation menus, featured images, a content slider, crisp typography, and support for post excerpts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Writee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee.jpg\" alt=\"Writee\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224136\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Writee is a simple and free theme for personal WordPress websites and blogs. It has features to support writers and bloggers. Writee works great with all the third-party <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Plugins that You MUST Use (2018)\">WordPress plugins that you must have</a> on your blog. It has an image slider that integrates with your posts to show the featured content on your homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence.jpg\" alt=\"Presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224137\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Presence is a WordPress theme for business websites. It&#8217;s easy to use and offers ready-made demo websites to quickly launch your business site. It has a simple design that can be used to create any professional website like hotel, restaurant, music, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)\">real estate</a>, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Roxima</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/roxima.jpg\" alt=\"Roxima\" width=\"775\" hei