.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/\">24 Best WordPress Themes for Membership Sites (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34844:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress themes for membership sites? Youve come to the right place. We know that, with the perfect theme, your membership site can maximize its earning potential. With the right set of features, you can increase memberships, up engagement, and create a business you can be proud of.</p>\n<p>Thats why weve handpicked the 26 best WordPress themes for membership sites. Each one is fully responsive, so itll look great on any device. </p>\n<p>Want a sneak peek? Check out our top 5 favorites in the table below!</p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-9\">At a Glance: Top WordPress Themes for Membership Sites</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-9\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-9\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Theme</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Unique Because...</th><th class=\"column-4\">Released By</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\" https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Divi</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$89/year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Shipped with a drag &amp; drop builder</td><td class=\"column-4\">Elegant Themes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ultra</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Bundled with numerous demo sites</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Public Opinion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Public Opinion</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best for Membership + Magazine Design</td><td class=\"column-4\">CSSIgniter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shoppe\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shoppe</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Perfect for WooCommerce websites</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\">Float</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Supports parallax scrolling</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-9 from cache -->\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi.jpg\" alt=\"divi\" width=\"748\" height=\"305\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225639\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-300x122.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The first theme were going to look at is a jack-of-all-trades theme called Divi. This intuitive theme is perfect for WordPress veterans and newbies alike with its collection of premade theme layouts as well as the ability to build your own theme using their tools from the ground up. </p>\n<p>Divi comes with a host of mix-and-match features, allowing you to freely dip into their 46 different elements, pick what you like, and customize them to fit your site and your brand. </p>\n<p>The fast loading times and instant updates as you tweak and edit your website make this theme an excellent choice for those who want to try something brand new and give their membership site a custom feel in a short amount of time. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Divi Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Themify Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra.png\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"272\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225640\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra-768x270.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Are you looking for a large collection of professional, handcrafted themes? If so, Themify Ultra is right up your alley! This <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\">premium responsive theme</a> comes with a whopping 60 custom demos for you to choose from that will instantly spruce up your site.</p>\n<p>The excitement doesn&#8217;t end there! After youve picked a preselected layout you can go in and make it your own. Theres nothing like being able to add your own touch to an already brilliant theme, and Themify Ultra allows you that freedom. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Ultra Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Public Opinion</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion.jpg\" alt=\"public opinion\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225641\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Public Opinion, as the name implies, is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-blog-themes/\">WordPress magazine theme</a> set designed for webmasters who have newspaper/magazine-themed web pages. The customization options are vast, giving you the chance to build your magazine brand from scratch. </p>\n<p>You can choose from 30 different color options, use an array of layouts that match the style your readers enjoy, and it also gives you just the right amount of space to include advertisements for additional revenue and promotions. </p>\n<p>Once youve finished your layout, you can add unique widgets based on the core design of your site. Finally, youll get the option to add your own modules so its truly a custom creation. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Public Opinion Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Themify Shoppe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe.png\" alt=\"shoppe\" width=\"775\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225642\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe-300x147.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe-768x377.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Setting up your first eCommerce website doesnt have to take a specialist when you have this amazing membership theme at your fingertips. They proudly boast that Themify Shoppe allows you to build your website shop and theme in mere minutes.</p>\n<p>You can use Themify Shoppe to tailor your customers experience and keep them coming back for more. Its a breeze to add things like a wish list, quick-look features, and even an Ajax cart for speedy checkouts. </p>\n<p>Combine those amazing tools with the ability to tweak and build upon existing layouts, and its no wonder why Themify Shoppe made it onto our list of the best WordPress themes for membership sites! </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Shoppe Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Themify Float</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.png\" alt=\"float\" width=\"775\" height=\"267\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225643\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-300x103.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-768x265.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Themify Float is what some would call the futuristic version of the Themifys membership themes. The centerpiece is the ability to use parallax images throughout the design template