licit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13632:\"<p>Are you looking for the best download manager plugins for WordPress? Good idea! While WordPress websites allow you to upload files and place download links in your posts and pages, theres no default way to scale them. Whereas, with a download manager plugin, you can track, manage, and control permissions for your file downloads. You can even use them to SELL file downloads, if you wish!</p>\n<p>Thats why, in this article, weve handpicked the 7 best download manager plugins for WordPress! Check them out, choose your perfect match, and get ready to love the results.</p>\n<h3>Choosing the Best WordPress Download Manager Plugin</h3>\n<p>There are different types of download manager plugins. While some plugins let you track file downloads on your WordPress site, others provide secure access to files. </p>\n<p>Just because youre offering file downloads on your site, doesnt mean you need all sort of download manager plugins. Before you dive in and choose a download manager for your site, its essential for you to examine the purpose, so you dont waste your money on the wrong plugin. </p>\n<p>Ask yourself a few questions. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do you need to track WordPress downloads?</li>\n<li>Do you want to provide a secure access to the file?</li>\n<li>Do you want to sync your files to Dropbox or Google Drive?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now that youve got a basic idea, lets go ahead and view the top 7 download manager plugins for WordPress. </p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-6\">At a Glance: 7 Best Download Manager Plugins</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-6\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-6\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Plugin</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Active Installs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">From $79.60/year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Over 2 million</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress File Download Manager</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$17</td><td class=\"column-3\">1,400+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Multiverso</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$30</td><td class=\"column-3\">1,100+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Easy Digital Downloads</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">60,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress Download Manager</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">100,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download Attachments</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">10,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-8 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Delightful Downloads</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">10,000+</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-6 from cache -->\n<h3><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\">1. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221490\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is number 1 on this list for good reason. Not only is it the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/\">best Google Analytics tool</a> on the market, its also the best download manager plugin for WordPress.</p>\n<p>With just a few clicks, you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/\">set up Google Analytics on your WordPress website</a> and get access to things like real-time stats, eCommerce tracking, ads tracking, referral tracking, popular posts tracking, forms tracking, and more! Its GDPR compliant, wont slow down your site, and all the reports you need can be accessed from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p>Now, with the File Downloads Tracking addon, you can utilize MonsterInsights as a download manager plugin as well! Need help getting started? Check out our tutorial on how to set up download tracking in Google Analytics using Monster Insights.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with MonsterInsights Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. WordPress File Download Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress File Download Manager\" width=\"694\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225026\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager.jpg 694w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Need to give your clients access to confidential files in a secure way? Then the WordPress File Download Manager is the plugin for you.</p>\n<p>Your WordPress site users can login and download the files youve assigned specifically to them. Even if the file download is a URL, this highly secured plugin will ensure that only the assigned user can download the file.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WordPress File Download Manager Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Multiverso Advanced File Sharing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso.jpg\" alt=\"Multiverso\" width=\"697\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225027\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso.jpg 697w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 697px) 100vw, 697px\" /></a></p>\n<p>An advanced file sharing plugin with developer-friendly features, Multiverso lets you create a file sharing section on your WordPress website thats accessible to the user roles you allow, from administrators to subscribers.</p>\n<p>Set your security checks, file upload size, categories, and more. Theres also plenty of shortcodes as well as sexy jQuery options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Multiverso Advanced File Sharing Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Easy Digital Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"190\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225028\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads-300x74.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads-768x188.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If youve got an eCommerce website and youre selling digital downloads, then Easy Digital Downloads is the perfect plugin for you. You can track anything from eBooks, to photos, to documents, to songs with this complete selling system.</p>\n<p>Available in over 24 languages, EDD makes it easy to jump into selling and managing your downloads, no matter where you are in the world. </p>\n<p>This free plugin integrates with PayPal, Amazon Payments, Stripe, Authorize.net, BitPay, and more. Need even more options? Their premium extensions give you access to even more payment gateways, email service integrations, and file management options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Easy Digital Downloads Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WordPress Download Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress Download Manager\" width=\"775\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225029\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager-300x109.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager-768x278.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Manage, track, and take complete control of your file downloads with the WordPress Download Manager plugin. Keep your files secure by assigning them to user roles, or by setting passwords.</p>\n<p>For eCommerce sites, there are options to set up licenses, prices, download limits, and more. It also integrates with DropBox, OneDrive, Google Drive, and more.</p>\n<p>Secure and translation-ready, this free plugin is easy to set up and use with multiple useful features.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Download Manager Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Download Attachments</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments.jpg\" alt=\"Download Attachments\" width=\"775\" height=\"278\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225030\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments-300x108.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments-768x275.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Download Attachments is one of the best download manager plugins because it makes use of AJAX and a simple drag and drop interface. We love simplicity.</p>\n<p>However, if youre a developer and wish to expand Download Attachments features, youll love their multiple filter hooks and functions.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Download Attachments Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Delightful Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads.jpg\" alt=\"Delightful Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"261\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225031\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads-300x101.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads-768x259.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This developer-friendly plugin is free to download and use, and lets you easily add download buttons and links to pages, posts, and wigetized areas.</p>\n<p>Best of all, your download statistics and reports can be found directly inside your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Delightful Downloads Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best download manager plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this post, you might also like our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 Best WordPress Security Plugins Compared (2018)\">6 best WordPress security plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/\">7 Best Download Manager Plugins Compared (Fast &#038; Secure)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 10 Dec 2018 10:01:22 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"how to create an online store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"how to integrate shopify with wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"how to start an online store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=225323\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:609:\"<p>Are you wondering how to integrate Shopify with WordPress? For WordPress beginners, it might seem difficult to turn your WordPress site into an online store, but it&#8217;s not. Starting an online shop is easier than ever before with Shopify and WordPress. Anyone can build a beautiful online shop in no time and start selling right [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\">How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22700:\"<p>Are you wondering how to integrate Shopify with WordPress? For WordPress beginners, it might seem difficult to turn your WordPress site into an online store, but it&#8217;s not. Starting an online shop is easier than ever before with Shopify and WordPress. Anyone can build a beautiful online shop in no time and start selling right away, without knowing a thing about code. </p>\n<p>So, are you ready to build your own online store and start selling immediately? </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to integrate Shopify with WordPress, step-by-step. </p>\n<h3>Why Integrate Shopify with WordPress?</h3>\n<p>WordPress offers several <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\">eCommerce plugins</a>, like WooCommerce, to help you start an online shop. </p>\n<p>Maybe you&#8217;re wondering why you should choose <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shopify</a> over the other eCommerce plugins? Below are a few advantages of using Shopify as your storefront:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ease of use </strong>: Getting started with Shopify is much easier than using native WordPress eCommerce plugins. All you have to do is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">sign up for an account with Shopify</a> to get your online shop up and running. You also don&#8217;t have to worry about site speed or security, because Shopify takes care of all of that for you.</li>\n<li><strong>Reduced overhead</strong>: Shopify is a cloud-based solution, so you won&#8217;t experience traffic outages as your business grows. This means you don&#8217;t have to worry about running out of server resources and upgrading to more expensive WordPress hosting.</li>\n<li><strong>Easy social media integration</strong>: Integrating your online store with social media is important for marketing your business and products. Shopify&#8217;s app store makes it easy. They have apps to integrate your Instagram feed on your site, add social media sharing buttons, and more. All you have to do is download the apps of your choosing, no coding required. </li>\n<li><strong>Better shopping cart options</strong>: Shopify offers built-in payment options so you can instantly take payments from Visa, Mastercard, Discover, and American Express. They also offer multiple payment gateways like PayPal, and they&#8217;ll automatically calculate shipping rates and taxes for you so you can easily ship to anywhere in the world.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Who Should Use Shopify with WordPress?</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a> is a good choice for online selling beginners and experienced sellers alike. But Shopify is especially great for beginners because it&#8217;s a lot easier to use. Unlike WooCommerce, you don&#8217;t have to install anything and you can get started quickly. </p>\n<p>They also have easy-to-understand pricing plans. Shopify&#8217;s basic plan starts at $29 per month. You don&#8217;t have to worry about spending too much money on hosting plans and optimization for your online store. With their basic plan, you can minimize the risks of starting an online shop. And, as your online business grows, you can upgrade your plan to match your needs. </p>\n<p>Shopify is the platform for you if you want a solution that&#8217;s completely <strong>hassle-free</strong> and is <strong>limitless in terms of scalability</strong> for your online shop. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1.jpg\" alt=\"how to add shopify to wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"319\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1-300x129.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d still rather use WooCommerce with WordPress, check out our tutorial: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\">How to Create an Online Store with WooCommerce- Step-by-Step</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s dive into how to integrate Shopify with WordPress.   </p>\n<h3>Set Up Shopify with WordPress &#8211; Step-by-Step</h3>\n<p>Integrating <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shopify</a> with your WordPress site is as easy as embedding the code snippet. Let&#8217;s take a look at the step-by-step guide below. </p>\n<h3>Step 0: Start a Website on WordPress</h3>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t already have a WordPress website, you&#8217;ll need to create one in order to start an online shop with Shopify. WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world, it&#8217;s the best platform to start a website. It comes with a number of built-in features that&#8217;ll help you easily build a website without having to know anything about code. </p>\n<p>There&#8217;re a number of steps to starting a website on WordPress. First, you&#8217;ll need to pick a domain name for your business. A domain name, or URL, is your site&#8217;s address online. We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Nameboy</a> to help find the perfect domain name for your online shop. </p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-hosting/\">choose a website host</a>. A web host is the business that provides the technologies and services a website needs to be viewed on the internet. It&#8217;s where your website files are stored. In other words, if your domain name is your address; your web hosting is your house.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Bluehost</a> to set up your online store. Bluehost is one of the best website hosting services available and they offer 1-click WordPress installation so you can create your online shop super fast.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress.png\" alt=\"start-a-website-bluehost\" width=\"740\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225328\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve negotiated a deal with Bluehost to offer our users a free domain name, free SSL, and over 60% off on WordPress hosting.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>If you want more detailed instructions on how to start a website on WordPress, check out our tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">how to make a website &#8211; step-by-step</a>. </p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve got a domain name, a web hosting, installed WordPress, and built your website, you&#8217;re ready to integrate Shopify and start selling.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Set up a Shopify Store</h3>\n<p>The first step to integrating Shopify with WordPress is to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">set up an account with Shopify</a>. Head over to the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a> website. On their home page, you&#8217;ll see an area where you can enter your email address to start a free 14-day trial. After typing in your email address, press the <strong>Get Started</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2.png\" alt=\"set-up-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"238\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225331\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll be prompted to choose a password for you account and your store name as well. When you&#8217;ve finished entering in the information, click on the <strong>Create your store</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password.png\" alt=\"how-to-integrate-shopify-with-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225334\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password-300x167.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then, you&#8217;ll be asked to answer a couple questions from Shopify so they can get to know your needs better. Click on the dropdown arrow to choose your answers to the questions and then click <strong>Next</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1.png\" alt=\"set-up-shopify-with-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"447\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225335\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1-300x181.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>In the next area, you&#8217;ll be requested to fill in your name, address, phone number, and website address. When you&#8217;ve finished filling out this part, click the <strong>Enter my store</strong> button at the bottom of the form. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2.png\" alt=\"setting-up-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"534\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225336\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2-300x216.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll then be redirected to the home page of your Shopify account. Your Shopify store is now ready for you. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard.png\" alt=\"shopify-dashboard\" width=\"740\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225338\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard-300x144.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 2: Set up Payments and Shipping for Your Shopify Store</h3>\n<p>In order to accept payments from customers, you&#8217;ll need to set up payments for your Shopify store. To do so, click on <strong>Settings</strong> in the bottom corner of your home page and then click on <strong>Payment providers</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments.png\" alt=\"shopify-set-up-payments\" width=\"740\" height=\"329\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225340\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments-300x133.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Your Shopify account is automatically set up to receive PayPal payments with PayPal Express Checkout. If you have a PayPal account set up already with the email address you used to create your Shopify account, you should be ready to accept payments. If you don&#8217;t have a PayPal account, Shopify will send you an email with instructions on how to set up a PayPal Merchant account to claim your funds.   </p>\n<p>For the ability to accept other forms of payment from customers like credit cards, you&#8217;ll need to click on the <strong>Complete account setup</strong> button to provide Shopify with more details about your business. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers.png\" alt=\"how-to-set-up-shopify-payments\" width=\"740\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225344\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers-300x154.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also choose to accept alternative forms of payment like BitPay and GoCoin as well.</p>\n<p>The last step to setting up your Shopify store so it&#8217;s ready to start selling is to set up shipping. Click on the <strong>Settings</strong> button again and then click on <strong>Shipping</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping.png\" alt=\"shopify-shipping-set-up\" width=\"740\" height=\"325\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225345\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping-300x132.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>By default, the shipping origin will be set to the store address you entered in when setting up your Shopify account. You can edit the shipping origin if you wish by clicking the <strong>Change shipping origin</strong> button. </p>\n<p>In this area, you can also define shipping zones and rates for shipping to those locations. If you don&#8217;t know how much to charge for shipping, try contacting your local post office to get some advice. </p>\n<h3>Step 3: Add Your Products to Shopify</h3>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to add your products to your Spotify account. To add your products, click on the <strong>Products</strong> tab in the menu on the right and then click on <strong>Add product</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products.png\" alt=\"add products to shopify\" width=\"740\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225356\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products-300x130.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then fill out all of the information about your product including the name/title of your product, product description, price, and more. Upload a high-quality image of your product here as well. You can also add the product to a collection to make it easier to find in your store. When you&#8217;re finished filling in all of the details for your product, click the <strong>Save</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct.png\" alt=\"add-products-to-your-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225357\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Repeat this step for all of the products you offer. </p>\n<h3>Step 4: Choosing Your Shopify Pricing Plan</h3>\n<p>Now that you&#8217;ve got the basics of your Shopify account configured, you&#8217;ll have to choose a pricing plan to actually get your online store up and running. Click on the <strong>Select a plan</strong> button in the banner at the bottom of your screen.  </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan.png\" alt=\"shopify-plan\" width=\"740\" height=\"397\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan-300x161.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll then be presented with 3 different plan options. If you&#8217;re just starting out and new to selling online, we recommend choosing the Basic Shopify plan for $29 per month. You can always upgrade your plan anytime you want if you need more features or if your online store grows quickly. To choose the Basic Shopify plan, click the <strong>Choose this plan</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2.png\" alt=\"setting up shopify with wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"445\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225354\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then enter your credit card information and press the <strong>Start plan</strong> button.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with Shopify Today!</a> </p>\n<p>Now you&#8217;re ready to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" target=\"_blank\">start making money online</a> with Shopify and your WordPress site. </p>\n<h3>Step 5: Using Shopify Buy Button</h3>\n<p>Now it&#8217;s time to integrate Shopify with your WordPress site with Buy Buttons. Buy Buttons link to your Shopify checkout and they&#8217;re included in all Shopify plans. Buy Buttons allow you to sell your products on your website or in blog posts. You can also use Buy Buttons to create a checkout link to send to customers in email messages or on social media. </p>\n<p>If the Buy Button sales channel doesn&#8217;t appear in the Sales Channel section of your Shopify admin, you&#8217;ll need to add it. To add the Buy Button sales channel, click on <strong>Settings</strong> and then click on the <strong>Sales channels</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel.png\" alt=\"adding shopify to wordpress with buy button\" width=\"740\" height=\"332\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225358\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel-300x135.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Add sales channel</strong> button. You&#8217;ll then see a list of available sales channels, scroll down to find the <strong>Buy Button</strong> channel. Once you find it, click the blue <strong>+</strong> button to install. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton.png\" alt=\"how to install buy button to integrate shopify and wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"402\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225359\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>After installing the Buy Button sales channel, click on the <strong>Create Buy Button</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button.png\" alt=\"create shopify buy button\" width=\"740\" height=\"373\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225361\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button-300x151.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, pick the product you want to create a buy button for and click the <strong>Select product</strong> button. Now you can configure the look of your Buy Button. You can choose a template, customize the button color and text, and the action that happens when a customer clicks the button. When you&#8217;re finished customizing the appearance of your button, click the <strong>Generate code</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation-.png\" alt=\"shopify product buy button for wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"589\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225362\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation-.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation--300x239.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>The next step is to copy the code and add it to your WordPress site. </p>\n<h3>Step 6: Add Shopify Buy Buttons to Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>Now we need to add your products to your WordPress site so you can start selling them. Click the <strong>Copy code to clipboard</strong> button to copy the code you just generated for that product. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code.png\" alt=\"add-shopify-product-to-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"409\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225363\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code-300x166.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can paste this code anywhere on your website where you want your Buy Button to appear. For example, you can create a page on your WordPress site to display your Buy Buttons. Create the page on WordPress, name it, and then paste the code. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress.png\" alt=\"how to add shopify buy buttons to wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"408\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225364\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also paste the code in <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/50-blog-post-ideas-that-you-can-write-about-today/\" target=\"_blank\">blog posts</a> or in your WordPress sidebar. </p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Integrating Shopify with WordPress is that easy. Now that you know how to add Shopify to your WordPress site, you&#8217;ll be attracting customers and making a ton of sales in no time.</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoyed this article. If you did, take a look at our article on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\">9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, Fast!</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\">How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"AffiliateWP Review  Affiliate Program for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 07 Dec 2018 11:20:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=225678\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:615:\"<p>Looking to create an affiliate program for your product? An affiliate program is a referral system where you incentivize others to refer your product by offering them a commission for every sale they refer. How do you create an affiliate system in WordPress? Thats what the AffiliateWP plugin was created for. It enables you to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\">AffiliateWP Review  Affiliate Program for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22879:\"<p>Looking to create an affiliate program for your product? An affiliate program is a referral system where you incentivize others to refer your product by offering them a commission for every sale they refer.</p>\n<p>How do you create an affiliate system in WordPress? Thats what the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> plugin was created for. It enables you to create a full-fledged affiliate system in WordPress with ease. If you want to know more about its features, functionalities, pricing, etc., continue reading our complete AffiliateWP review below. </p>\n<h3>About the AffiliateWP Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"427\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225686\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress-300x165.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress-768x423.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is the #1 affiliate management system plugin for WordPress. It allows you to build a complete affiliate system in WordPress and helps to manage affiliates, referrals, payments, etc. from your site. It comes with all the affiliate marketing tools you&#8217;ll need to grow your business and earn money. </p>\n<p>Its a plugin built for WordPress that looks and feels like WordPress itself. All of its features are carefully-designed to adapt with WordPress and to give you a familiar experience. Plus, it comes with advanced affiliate and referral tracking features that provide reliable, accurate data. </p>\n<p>AffiliateWP was developed by the same team who created the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> eCoommerce plugin. Therefore, the plugin has seamless integration with Easy Digital Downloads. Not to mention, it also has full support for WooCommerce and other popular membership, form, and invoice plugins. </p>\n<h3>How Does Affiliate Marketing Work?</h3>\n<p>Affiliate marketing is one of the most popular ways to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\">make money online</a>. Affiliate marketing creates a win-win situation for the 2 parties involved; the business owners and the affiliates. Its the collaboration in which affiliates help to sell more products and business owners offer a commission to affiliates for each sale they referred to. </p>\n<p>For example, if youre a business owner and trying to sell products, you can create an affiliate system on your site and appeal affiliates to join. When they become an affiliate of your website, they pick products from your store and promote them on their blog and various other platforms. Now if people come to your store via the affiliate links and buy a product, the affiliate who referred the customer gets a certain percent commission. </p>\n<p>As a business owner, your store will get more visibility, more traffic, and more sales. On the other hand, affiliates will earn money for each sale they referred to your store. Therefore, its rewarding to both businesses and affiliate marketers. </p>\n<p>So, if youre running an online store but dont have an affiliate program, you definitely need to consider having one. </p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Review  Getting Started with AffiliateWP</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is a plugin exclusively designed for WordPress with an interface just like the native WordPress interface. Its therefore easy to configure and use. </p>\n<p>First, download the plugin file from the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">official AffiliateWP website</a> and install it on your site. If you need detailed instructions, heres our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\">how to install a plugin</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>1. General Settings</strong></p>\n<p>After the plugin is activated, navigate to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Settings</strong> to activate your plugin license. You can find the license key in your account on the AffiliteWP website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-general-setting\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225687\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>In addition to license activation, the <strong>General</strong> tab has a number of affiliate settings. You can select an affiliate page or affiliate agreement page; however, feel free to leave them as they are because these pages are automatically created by the plugin to meet affiliate-specific needs. </p>\n<p>Next, you can configure referral settings. The referral variable by default is <strong>ref</strong> and the default referral format looks like this: <strong>https://yoursite.com/?ref=1</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings.jpg\" alt=\"referral-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"223\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225688\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings-300x86.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings-768x221.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to change the referral variable, you can use <strong>aff, refer, partner</strong>, etc. </p>\n<p>Next, you can enable <strong>Pretty Affiliate URLs</strong> which will replace the query strings (i.e. ?ref=) and change your URL format to <strong>https://yoursite.com/ref/1</strong>.</p>\n<p>You can select a referral rate type from either a percentage or a flat amount. Then, you can add a referral rate. Also review <strong>Exclude Shipping</strong> and <strong>Exclude Tax</strong> options. Then, you can also add a cookie expiration duration; for example, 30 days (which means that a purchase within 30 days of users visit via a referral link will be valid for the commission). </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review.jpg\" alt=\"referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225689\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you review all the options, dont forget to click <strong>Save Changes</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Integrations</strong></p>\n<p>The plugin has inbuilt integration for a number of eCommerce, membership, form, and invoice plugins and systems. You can enable the ones you need easily from <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Settings &raquo; Integrations</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings.jpg\" alt=\"integrations-affiliatewp-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225690\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>3. Email Settings</strong></p>\n<p>You can configure all the email settings from the <strong>Email</strong> tab in AffiliateWP settings. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"email-settings-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225691\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can upload a logo, choose an email template, from name and email, etc. Then, you can configure notification emails on new affiliate registrations, affiliate application accepted, referral awarded, affiliate application being reviewed, and application rejected. </p>\n<p><strong>4. Miscellaneous Settings</strong></p>\n<p>The <strong>Misc</strong> tab in AffiliateWP settings allow you to configure different options useful for your affiliate system. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"misc-settings-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225692\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can enable or disable affiliate registration by the user themselves, affiliate approval required, reCAPTCHA, and much more. </p>\n<p>Review all the settings, and then click <strong>Save Changes</strong> to save your settings. </p>\n<h3>Creating the Affiliate Area</h3>\n<p>Affiliate Area is where your users can see the affiliate registration and login form. Via this page, new affiliate marketers apply for your affiliate program whereas already signed-up affiliates can log into their accounts, generate referral links, view stats, and see their earnings. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP plugin</a> automatically creates an <strong>Affiliate Area</strong> page right when you install the plugin into WordPress. If you dont find this page, you can create a new page yourself and add the shortcode <strong>[affiliate_area]</strong> in the main content area, then itll create the affiliate area page for you. </p>\n<p>Take a look at the screenshot below to see how your Affiliate Area will look: </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area\" width=\"268\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225693\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area.jpg 268w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-115x300.jpg 115w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 268px) 100vw, 268px\" /></p>\n<p>When a user logs into their account, theyll see a different Affiliate Area. The Affiliate Area for logged-in users looks like the screenshot below: </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"689\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225694\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp-300x267.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp-768x683.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Affiliates can generate affiliate URLs by entering a page URL in the field there and clicking on the <strong>Generate URL</strong> button. </p>\n<p>Next, the <strong>Statistics</strong> option shows a summary of paid and unpaid referrals, visits, conversion rate, earnings, and commission rates. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-statistics\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225695\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon clicking on the next option, <strong>Graphs</strong>, affiliates can see a graphical presentation of the affiliate statistics. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-graphs\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225696\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Referrals</strong> provides a glimpse of the affiliates referrals with the amount earned, product description, and status as paid or unpaid.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-referrals\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225697\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The <strong>Visits</strong> option shows the pages visited by their affiliate links. </p>\n<p>The <strong>Creatives</strong> option includes promotional banners which affiliates can use on their blogs and multiple other platforms to promote your products.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-creatives\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225698\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>And, finally, the <strong>Settings</strong> tab lets your affiliates add their payment email where you can send the commissions they earn.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"433\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225699\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings-768x429.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The Affiliate Area looks very clean and simple. Affiliate marketers will love your affiliate program interface. </p>\n<h3>Managing Your Affiliate Program</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> provides you with simple-yet-powerful options to manage your affiliate program. You can add, edit, and review affiliates; view individual and total affiliate reports; manage referrals, visits, and creative aspects; and view full reports on everything. </p>\n<p>Configuring and managing the admin options is easy with AffiliateWP. To get started, you can take a look at the overview of your affiliate system by going to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Overview</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"admin-overview-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225700\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can see the totals for paid earnings, unpaid referrals, most valuable affiliates, latest affiliate registrations, recent referrals, etc. in the Overview. </p>\n<p>Next, you can go to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Affiliate</strong> to view your list of all affiliates, add new affiliates, edit, etc. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225701\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The entire affiliate management works just like standard posts in WordPress. </p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Addons</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP plugin</a> comes with powerful free and premium addons which you can use to make your affiliate program more effective. In addition, it also supports a number of third-party addons. </p>\n<p>Therere 15 official free addons and 14 pro addons. The pro addons include PayPal Payouts, Recurring Referrals, Lifetime Commissions, Affiliate Landing Pages, etc. The free addons allow you to add features like display a leaderboard, showing attributed affiliate coupons, pay affiliates with store credit, etc. </p>\n<p>You can access the addons from your WordPress dashboard by visiting <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Addons</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-addons\" width=\"775\" height=\"619\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225702\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons-300x240.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons-768x613.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Plugin: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is a premium plugin that offers 4 pricing plans. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"308\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225703\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing-300x119.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing-768x305.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>1. Personal</strong>: It costs $99 per year. You can use it on 1 website only. Includes 15 official free addons and all AffiliateWP&#8217;s core features. </p>\n<p><strong>2. Plus</strong>: It costs $149 per year. It provides 3 site licenses. It also includes all free addons and core features of the plugin.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Professional</strong>: It costs $249 per year. You can use AffiliateWP on unlimited sites with this plan. It includes all 15 pro addons along with all the free official addons. </p>\n<p><strong>4. Ultimate</strong>: Its priced at $499 and its a one-time payment plan. With this plan, you can use AffiliateWP on unlimited sites. It also includes all pro and free addons and also future addons. </p>\n<p>With the 3 yearly subscription plans, youll get email support and updates for the duration of your current subscription whereas youll get lifetime support and updates with the <strong>Ultimate</strong> plan. </p>\n<p>If you have any questions, you can use their live chat for instant replies. You can also submit a ticket for support queries but you may not need to contact support because they have detailed documentation with really comprehensive articles to guide you. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using AffiliateWP for Creating a Affiliate System in WordPress</h3>\n<p>AffiliateWP is undoubtedly the number 1 best affiliate management system plugin for WordPress. It has a complete set of features and functionalities to allow you to create a powerful affiliate system in WordPress. Its integration with eCommerce, membership, forms, and invoice plugins make it the all-in-one solution for affiliate programs. </p>\n<p>The plugin was created just for WordPress which makes it a very special product. Its interface is very similar to the WordPress interface so anyone using WordPress will recognize the familiar feel of it and configure everything very easily. Its a simple plugin that you can use without touching any code. </p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is the best affiliate management plugin for creating and running an affiliate program on WordPress sites. Its a great tool you can use to boost your sales, improve SEO, and grow your business. </p>\n<p>We give it 4.5 out of 5 stars. Heres the breakdown of our review score:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\">AffiliateWP Review  Affiliate Program for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0: